      "span_text": "Lysosome Dysfunction Induced by Adenosine Accumulation in Lysosomes-Because TRPML1 is important for lysosome function [CITATION_1] , to test whether adenosine accumulation impairs lysosomal function, we first monitored lysosomal pH using LysoTracker Red DND-99."
